entries.femaleVariant: [Open trunk]
O-o-oh, it's not him. Thank God.
Quick, let me out before he returns!
[Close trunk]
What are you doing in here?
Unusual, as far as presents go.
W-what?! No!
Let me out! I-I can pay!
It's complicated. Hop out 'fore I change my mind.
I do not know what is going on, but thank you. You will not regret this.
And you are...?
Unusual – as far as presents go.
Help! Is anyone out there?
Someone! Someone! Please, help me!
Let me out!
Wha--? What did you say?
You're supposed to be my present – a surprise from a certain Sergei.
entries.maleVariant: Heheh, you're supposed to be my present – a surprise from a certain Sergei.

entries.femaleVariant: You're not making any sense!
Y'know, like a pop-out cake. 'Cept there's no cake – just lots of blood.
entries.maleVariant: Y'know, like a pop-out cake. Except there's no cake – just lots of blood.

entries.femaleVariant: Alex Pushkin, Senior Assistant in Quality Assurance at Biotechnica.
What's a corpo QA doin' messin' with the Tyger Claws?
Y-you work for Tyger Claws? I-I told them I-I would not accept their offer.
[Let Alex out] It's complicated. Hop out.
Sorry, bud, but your fate's been sealed.
[Close trunk] Looks like your fate's already been sealed.
Biotechnica? You know Joanne Koch?
You got this job from Wakako, yes? I will pay her. She won't lose an eddie – and neither will you!
Biotechnica, huh? Assumin' you know Joanne Koch.
I do, I do! Did a preem little project with her out in the Badlands. What about you?
Yeah, heard all about that project. Real triumph... Wonder how many from Red Ocher died – you recall?
Ugh, who can keep track? Besides, they're like roaches. Disgusting things will just multiply again.
[Free Alex] Get outta here. Before I change my mind.
[Shut trunk] Guess it's not your lucky day.
Not your lucky day after all.
Get the fuck outta my sight. And quick – before I change my mind.
What? Did I say... Wait! W-we must have other mutual friends!
